#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Features</title>"
msgstr "<title>Functies</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: features.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Features</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Functies</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most important features and improvements are highlighted here, it would "
"make this list too long if we were to include <emphasis>all</emphasis> the "
"features and improvements. You will discover even more features in this "
"documentation and in the <ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/krusader?"
"path=ChangeLog\"><filename>ChangeLog</filename></ulink> and <ulink url="
"\"https://commits.kde.org/krusader?path=NEWS\"><filename>NEWS</filename></"
"ulink> files."
msgstr ""
"Hier vindt u de belangrijkste functies en verbeteringen, de lijst wordt te "
"lang als we <emphasis>alle</emphasis> functies en verbeteringen moeten "
"opnoemen. U zal zelf nog meer functies in deze documentatie en in deze "
"bestanden <ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/krusader?path=ChangeLog"
"\"><filename>ChangeLog</filename></ulink> en <ulink url=\"https://commits."
"kde.org/krusader?path=NEWS\"><filename>NEWS</filename></ulink> kunnen vinden."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.softpanorama.org/OFM/index.shtml\">Orthodox File "
"Manager (OFM)</ulink> features"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.softpanorama.org/OFM/index.shtml\">Orthodox "
"bestandsbeheerder (OFM)</ulink> functies"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two powerful and easy to use <link linkend=\"panels\">OFM panels</link>."
msgstr ""
"Twee krachtige en makkelijk te gebruiken <link linkend=\"panels\">OFM "
"panelen</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmdline\">Command Line</link> and optional <link linkend="
"\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</link> below."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmdline\">Commandoregel</link> en optioneel <link linkend="
"\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</link> eronder."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Strong <link linkend=\"keyboard-commands\">keyboard</link> orientation and "
"the ability to perform all functions without the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Sterke oriëntatie op het <link linkend=\"keyboard-commands\">toetsenbord</"
"link> met de mogelijkheid om zonder de muis all functies uit te voeren."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Context-dependent invocation of scripts and programs &eg; mouse click/"
"&Enter; (execute or open with the associated application), <keycap>F3</"
"keycap> (view) and <keycap>F4</keycap> (edit)."
msgstr ""
"Contextafhankelijke aanroeping van scripts en programma´s &eg; muisklik/"
"&Enter; (uitvoeren of openen met gekoppelde programma), <keycap>F3</keycap> "
"(weergave) en <keycap>F4</keycap> (bewerken)."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"useractions\">User Menu</link>, create your own customized "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"useractions\">Gebruikersmenu</link>, creëer uw eigen "
"aangepaste menu."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"History &eg; <link linkend=\"folderhistory\">Folder History</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"popular-urls\">Popular &URL;s</link>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Geschiedenis &eg; <link linkend=\"folderhistory\">Map geschiedenis</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"popular-urls\">Populaire &URL;s</link>, &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"vfs\">Virtual file systems (VFS)</link> &eg; for <link "
"linkend=\"remote-connections\">Remote Connections</link>, <link linkend="
"\"archives\">archives</link>, search results, synchronizer."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"vfs\">Virtuele bestandssystemen (VFS)</link> &eg; voor <link "
"linkend=\"remote-connections\">Externe verbindingen</link>, <link linkend="
"\"archives\">archieven</link>, zoekresultaten, synchronisatie."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Powerful internal <link linkend=\"krviewer\">viewer and editor</link> via "
"kparts supporting almost every file format."
msgstr ""
"Krachtige interne <link linkend=\"krviewer\">weergave-bewerkingsprogramma</"
"link> via kparts dat bijna elk bestandsformaat ondersteunt."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Advanced Search module</link>: searching in "
"archives and search content on remote file systems."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Geavanceerde zoek module</link>: zoeken in "
"archieven en zoekresultaten in bestandssystemen ver weg."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several Panel view modes via the <link linkend=\"sidebar\">Sidebar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Meerdere paneel weergave modes via de <link linkend=\"sidebar\">Zijbalk</"
"link>."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; tools"
msgstr "&krusader;-hulpmiddelen"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Remote Connections</link>: &FTP;/SAMBA "
"with SFTP/SCP support via KIO Slaves"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Externe verbindingen</link>: &FTP;/"
"SAMBA met SFTP/SCP ondersteuning via KIO Slaves"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"locate\">Locate</link> &GUI; frontend"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"locate\">Lokaliseren</link> &GUI;-frontend"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize Folders"
msgstr "Mappen synchroniseren"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount-Manager"
msgstr "Mount Manager"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disk Usage"
msgstr "Schijfgebruik"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Root mode"
msgstr "Root modus"

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; features"
msgstr "Mogelijkheden in &krusader;"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Archive Handling: browsing, unpack, pack, testing. Supported <link linkend="
"\"archives\">archives</link>: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, rar, "
"rpm, tar, zip and 7-zip."
msgstr ""
"Hanteren van archieven: bladeren, uitpakken, inpakken, testen. Ondersteunde "
"<link linkend=\"archives\">archieven</link> zijn: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, "
"gzip, iso, lha, rar, rpm, tar, zip en 7-zip."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"checksum\">Checksum Creation and Verification</link> "
"mechanism that supports md5, sha1, sha256, sha224, sha256, sha384, sha512, "
"tiger, whirlpool, cfv, and crc."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"checksum\">Aanmaak en controle van checksum</link> "
"mechanismes die md5, sha1, sha256, sha224, sha256, sha384, sha512, tiger, "
"whirlpool, cfv, en crc ondersteunen."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"calculate\">Calculate occupied space</link> of files and "
"folders, archives and remote filesystems."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"calculate\">Berekent benodigde ruimte</link> voor bestanden "
"en mappen, archieven en bestandssystemen op afstand."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-dir\">Directory comparison</link> and <link linkend="
"\"view-menu\">filtering</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-dir\">Vergelijken van mappen</link> en <link linkend="
"\"view-menu\">filtering</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-content\">Compare files by content</link> via "
"external diff programs like &kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/"
"applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</application></ulink> "
"or <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/\"><application>xxdiff</"
"application></ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-content\">Vergelijk bestanden op inhoud</link> met "
"de externe diff programma's zoals &kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://www.kde."
"org/applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</application></"
"ulink> of <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/\"><application>xxdiff</"
"application></ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"multi_rename\">Rename</link> files and folders via <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/utilities/krename/"
"\"><application>KRename</application></ulink>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"multi_rename\">Hernoemen</link> van bestanden en mappen via "
"<ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/utilities/krename/"
"\"><application>KRename</application></ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Completely supports drag'n'drop: drag from &konqueror; straight into a "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal> file, from &krusader;'s panel "
"into the trash bin, the desktop or into &konqueror;"
msgstr ""
"Ondersteunt volledig slepen-en-loslaten: slepen van &konqueror; direct in "
"een <literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal>-bestand, uit een paneel "
"van &krusader; naar de prullenbak, het bureaublad of in &konqueror;"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Preserve date</link> for local targets at "
"copy/move operations."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Datum behouden</link> voor lokale doelen "
"bij kopiëren/verplaatsen."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>F9</keycap> opens a <link linkend=\"tools-menu\">Terminal Window</"
"link> in the current folder."
msgstr ""
"<keycap>F9</keycap> opent een <link linkend=\"tools-menu\">Terminalvenster</"
"link> in de huidige map."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Easy editing of <link linkend=\"file-menu\">file permissions</link> and "
"ownership and <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-view\">Numeric Permissions</link>."
msgstr ""
"Makkelijk bewerken van <link linkend=\"file-menu\">bestand toegangsrechten</"
"link> en eigenaarschap en <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-view\">Numerieke "
"toegangsrechten</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Selection filters</link> used in &eg; "
"Synchronizer and KruSearcher."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Selectiefilters</link> gebruikt in &eg; "
"Synchronizer en KruSearcher."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jump-Back"
msgstr "Terugspringen"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"konfig-general\"> &MIME; type-aware</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-general\"> is zich bewust van het &MIME;-type</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Tabbed panels</link> and <link linkend="
"\"krviewer\">Tabbed Editor/Viewer</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Panelen met tabbladen</link> en <link linkend="
"\"krviewer\">Bewerker/Viewer met tabbladen</link>."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick search, select and filter"
msgstr "Snelle zoekactie, selecteren en filteren"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "File splitter"
msgstr "Bestand splitser"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse Gestures"
msgstr "Muisgebaren"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"list_panel\">Quick Navigation</link> in the Location Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"list_panel\">Snelle navigatie</link> in de Locatie werkbalk."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "WhatsThis Help function in favour of tooltips where reasonable."
msgstr ""
"Waar mogelijk heeft de WhatsThis Help functie de voorkeur ten opzichte van "
"tooltips."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sync-browsing"
msgstr "Synchroon-bladeren"

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customize &krusader; to your own needs"
msgstr "&krusader; naar wens aanpassen"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-startup\"> Konfigurator</link> &krusader;'s "
"configuration center."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-startup\"> Konfigurator</link> &krusader;'s "
"configuratie center."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Main Toolbar</link>, <link linkend="
"\"actions_toolbar\">Actions Toolbar</link> for user actions and bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Hoofdwerkbalk</link>, <link linkend="
"\"actions_toolbar\">Actiebalk</link> voor de acties en bladwijzers van de "
"gebruiker."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key-bindings"
msgstr "Toetsenbindingen"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Kleuren"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panel profiles"
msgstr "Paneel-profielen"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark-Manager"
msgstr "Bladwijzerbeheerder"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selection Modes"
msgstr "Selectie modussen"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many more features can be <link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">configured</link> "
"the way you like."
msgstr ""
"Veel andere onderdelen zijn <link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">instelbaar</"
"link> op de manier die u wilt."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; Extensions"
msgstr "Extensies van &krusader;"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "UserActions"
msgstr "GebruikerActies"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Profiles"
msgstr "Kleurprofielen"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key-binding Profiles"
msgstr "Sneltoetsprofielen"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Download and upload your favourite &krusader; extensions at <ulink url="
"\"https://store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Download en upload uw favoriete &krusader;-uitbreidingen op <ulink url="
"\"https://store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New features in the &krusader;-1.80.0 <quote>Final 3rd Stone</quote> release"
msgstr ""
"Nieuwe mogelijkheden in de &krusader;-1.80.0 <quote>Final 3rd Stone</quote> "
"release"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive improvements"
msgstr "Archief-verbeteringen"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Password support</link> for: arj, ace, rar and "
"zip. Passwords can be stored in <application>Kwallet</application>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Wachtwoord ondersteuning</link> voor: arj, ace, "
"rar en zip. Wachtwoorden kunt u opslaan in <application>Kwallet</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">7-zip support</link>, by external applications "
"<application>7z</application> and <application>7za</application>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">7-zip ondersteuning</link>, door de externe "
"programma´s <application>7z</application> en <application>7za</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Auto-detection support</link>, allowing you to "
"open <quote>hidden archives</quote> (&eg; <trademark class=\"registered"
"\">OpenOffice</trademark> documents)."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Ondersteuning voor automatische detectie</link>, "
"hiermee kunt <quote>verborgen archieven</quote> openen (&eg; <trademark "
"class=\"registered\">OpenOffice</trademark> documenten)."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Packing/unpacking is now in the background."
msgstr "Inpakken/uitpakken gebeurt nu op de achtergrond."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "Brief View"
msgstr "Korte weergave"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many improvements of the <link linkend=\"useractions\">UserActions</link> "
"system."
msgstr ""
"Vele verbeteringen in het <link linkend=\"useractions\">GebruikerActies</"
"link>systeem."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Countless usability enhancements, especially in Konfigurator and the heavily "
"reordered menubar."
msgstr ""
"Talloze verbeteringen in de bruikbaarheid, met name in Konfigurator en de "
"opnieuw ingedeelde menubalk."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Media button"
msgstr "Media knop"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy/Move: <link linkend=\"copying\">preserve all attributes</link> (time, "
"owner, group)."
msgstr ""
"Kopiëren/Verplaatsen: <link linkend=\"copying\">behoudt alle attributen</"
"link> (tijd, eigenaar, groep)."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-color\">Dim the colors of the inactive panel</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-color\">De kleuren van het inactieve venster dimmen</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Renaming a filename without extension, single instance mode, start to system "
"tray, check this out in <link linkend=\"konfigurator\">Konfigurator</link>"
msgstr ""
"Een bestandsnaam zonder extensie hernoemen, enkele instance modus, in "
"systeemvak starten, u kunt dit instellen in de <link linkend=\"konfigurator"
"\">Konfigurator</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configurable <link linkend=\"list_panel\">Atomic extensions</link>, so that "
"extensions like <literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal> are shown as "
"one part in the <guilabel>Ext Column</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Instelbare <link linkend=\"list_panel\">Atomisme extensies</link>, zodat "
"extensies zoals <literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal> als een geheel "
"in de <guilabel>Ext kolom</guilabel> worden getoond."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context menu for bookmarks and enable/disable special bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"Contextmenu voor bladwijzers en inschakelen/uitschakelen speciale "
"bladwijzers."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restyled <link linkend=\"menu-commands\">MenuBar</link>"
msgstr "gerestylede <link linkend=\"menu-commands\">Menubalk</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</link> enhancements bringing new "
"functions, new usages and new look."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</link> verbeteringen brengen "
"nieuwe functies, nieuwe gebruiksmogelijkheden en een nieuw uiterlijk."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizer</link> enhancements and parallel "
"threads for slow &FTP; servers."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronisatie</link> verbeteringen en "
"parallelle threads voor langzame &FTP; servers."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">Single instance mode</link>, <link linkend="
"\"konfig-startup\">start to system tray</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">Eén programma modus</link>, <link linkend="
"\"konfig-startup\">In systeemvak starten</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context menu for permanent bookmarks."
msgstr "Contextmenu voor permanente bladwijzers."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Full support for <link linkend=\"acl\">ACL permissions</link>, like "
"properties, preserve attributes, synchronizer and other."
msgstr ""
"Volledige ondersteuning voor <link linkend=\"acl\">ACL permissies</link>, "
"zoals eigenschappen, behoud van attributen, synchronisatie en anderen."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searcher-results, Locate-results, Synchronizer-results: support for dragging "
"items and copy to clipboard (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Zoekresultaten, Locatieresultaten, Synchronisatie-resultaten: ondersteuning "
"voor het verslepen van items en kopiëren naar klembord (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "Many bug fixes."
msgstr "Vele fouten gerepareerd."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New features in the &krusader;-1.90.0 <quote>Power Stone</quote> release"
msgstr ""
"Nieuwe mogelijkheden in de &krusader;-1.90.0 <quote>Power Stone</quote> "
